        'Agreed price then renegotiation: You agree MAD 30 before departing; the driver claims he said MAD 130 on arrival. Always confirm clearly and loudly before getting in.',
        'Fake guide drop-off: Driver "helpfully" stops near the medina and introduces his guide friend who offers to take you the rest of the way — for a large fee.',
